import { Card, CardContent, Grid, TextField, Typography } from "@mui/material"

export default function DepartamentoForm() {
  return (
    <Grid container direction='column' alignItems='center' justifyContent='center'>
      <Grid item xs={3}>
        <Card sx={{mt: 5}}>
          <Typography> Crear Departamento </Typography>
          <CardContent>
            <form>
              <TextField variant="filled" placeholder="Nombre Departamento" label="Nombre del Departamento" sx={{display: 'block', margin:'.5rem 0'}}></TextField>
            </form>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}
